   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Caregivers APP for 150 HD families in Colombia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This App will enable caregivers to access patient care guides, written and audio-visual, generated in a culturally-sensitive manner. The aim of this program is to strengthen the capabilities of informal caregivers and promote best practices of care for the Huntington&apos;s disease (HD) patients, including basic care practices, exercises to improve mobility, advice about nutrition, recipes, psychological support, and surveys on caregivers&apos; fatigue. Once launched, we hope to expand to other regions.</narrative>
  </description>
